{"tid":2390264,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"怎樣才算忠誠的遊戲驛站（GME）股東？","createTime":"2021-02-01T12:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T01:05:23.000Z","uid":133183,"like":60,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ed2dcdc53dc69ef5e6c5de50941ec3c5b108fe","tid":2390264,"uid":133183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"1，要在股價破頂時stronghold（SH）<br />\n2，要在公司內部出現利淡消息時stronghold（SH）<br />\n3，要在市場炒賣氣氛最好時stronghold（SH）<br />\n4，你不能高賣低買<br />\n5，你不能以日內交易（daytrade）賺取價差，你要一股不賣<br />\n6，你不能以任何槓桿工具買入，你要買正股創造需求，讓公司股價得以繼續上揚<br />\n7，在盤前時段，你不能交易股票，以免間接幫助基金大戶造市<br />\n8，每當GME破頂，你應該加倉，保證上升勢頭持續<br />\n9，每當GME高位盤整，你應該加倉，以示當前價格有力支持<br />\n10，每當GME被基金拋貨，你應該加倉，確保沽空一方無法以低價補回倉位<br />\n11，務必遵守以上守則，否則你提前獲利，忠誠的遊戲驛站股東會視你為背叛，指責你有錢唔識賺。我們希望您總是可以SH到底🤝"},{"pid":"081b0387198647636fbc84a7ca8320185b4fdce0","tid":2390264,"uid":100863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb4b41502fa8c20481ad8aef8c1e18f50246a34","tid":2390264,"uid":9974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e4cb4a55c6652d9b0946f71c8630b36d28e1b3","tid":2390264,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf88d046b14c8bcd97951e7ed57da8322f0cfec8","tid":2390264,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s